00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:39.010
lot at Lick Observatory.

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:40.110
So there they are.

00:01:40.110 --> 00:01:42.120
Just if you do this,
be very careful

00:01:42.120 --> 00:01:46.740
of all the crazy car drivers
